      "para_id": "Q001816.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Šu-Suen , the beloved of Enlil , the king whom Enlil chose with the love of his heart , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters , his beloved god , Habaluke , governor of Adab , his servant , built his beloved temple ."
    }
  ],
